{"tid":379282,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"TA同工發洩區","createTime":"2017-08-29T07:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T09:57:59.000Z","uid":5266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ed683b069f27ca4d384ecfa61bc4b46e861679e1","tid":379282,"uid":5266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T07:57:40.000Z","msg":"教育係好偉大 以生命影響生命<br />\n影響生命嘅同時 都係同時消磨緊自己生命同意志<br />\n想射波 麻煩到同事幫你安排代課 同時又會搞著幫你代課嘅同工<br />\n真係同時有幾個人心入面孖差緊你<br />\n好喇 如果你係TA 仲仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n假已經唔係跟學生假 <br />\n遇著仆街老細嘅話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你人工又小 大假得七日只可以係學生假到拎 （仲要簽左約先同我講要教班 我dllm)<br />\n去到大時大節 係人都知長假期啲機票酒店真係貴到喊出黎 平嘅就真係係正假期前後一日 <br />\n叫你搶一蚊機票你可以慳返啖氣<br />\n去台灣星馬泰日真係住同飛都先洗你45千蚊 （半份糧）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">最慘係你另一半仲要同你捱埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係呀 做得呢行預左架喇 純呻下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呻下咋 唔鐘意就負評喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81347045e0f12fc4523ff27eb800083e522720eb","tid":379282,"uid":48277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T07:58:33.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過係自己問題？"},{"pid":"0432ff52015fe7b94a030d6588d9be417c28154d","tid":379282,"uid":5266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T08:05:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇諗過係自己問題？</blockquote><br />\n無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所有野都如期交貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1e380ab160919422531e56a2fc6300fbf695586","tid":379282,"uid":87557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T08:05:23.000Z","msg":"好在我同事都好好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>有冇諗過係自己問題？</blockquote><br />\n我出生就係一個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e458f45760dc15b2afa0f2d5130e2531616ede67","tid":379282,"uid":5266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T08:09:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好在我同事都好好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>有冇諗過係自己問題？</blockquote><br />\n我出生就係一個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你唔得罪佢地 佢地咪好人囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但有啲真係好明顯係好難啃嘅工作<br />\n我個人會咒罵佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1320b87bf58556077c76b67b68897676027778bd","tid":379282,"uid":5266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T08:10:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好在我同事都好好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gi